title: Veeam Backup Jobs
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam Backup & Replication jobs via the REST API.

 It reports the job status, last result, and schedule information.

 The check returns:
 - OK: Job completed successfully
 - WARN: Job completed with warnings, or job is disabled
 - CRIT: Job failed
 - UNKNOWN: No data or job not found

 Optional parameters allow alerting on disabled jobs and
 maximum age of the last successful run.

item:
 The job name

discovery:
 One service is created for each backup job.
